Package swingtree.layout

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • swingtree.layout.Location
  • public final class Location
extends java.lang.Object
    An immutable value class that represents a location in a two-dimensional coordinate system specified in integer precision and specifically designed for Swing components. It can be used as an alternative to the AWT Point class, but in situations where immutability is desired.

    Use the of(float, float) factory method to create a new instance or withX(int) and withY(int) to create a new instance with a modified value.
